						               													<description>In Dystopia, zombies, tsunamis, viruses, atomic explosions threaten all continents.&amp;#10;Who among you will succeed in eliminating as many dangers as possible from their continent to save humanity?&amp;#10;Observation, memorization, deduction, cunning and strategy will be your best allies to win the game.&amp;#10;The goal: to have as few dangers as possible on his threatened continent to get out of it!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player chooses a continent.&amp;#10;On his turn either he takes the first card from the discard pile, or he takes the first card from the draw pile.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If he chooses a card face up he must swap it with a card from his deck and place it face up.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If he chooses a card from the draw pile, he chooses whether he keeps it or not.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If, at the end of his turn, a player thinks he has a minimum number of danger points, he announces &amp;quot;Dystopia&amp;quot;, which triggers the last turn, then the players reveal their cards and count the points.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
